overview: Adam (26), a bus driver from Surabaya - Jember, always works with Yudha (35) as a driver and Bagus (29) as a conductor with minimal income. At that time, Ana (23) who is Adam's girlfriend participated in the trip to Jember. Unexpectedly, Ana brought news that if Adam did not immediately propose he would be an arranged marriage.
title: Antar Kota Dalam Provinsi
